{{for|other uses|Weather Dependent Enemy}} '''Weather Dependent Enemies''' are enemies in {{XC3}} and {{XC3FR|sublink}}. They only appear during specific [[Weather (XC3)|weather]] events across [[Aionios]]. Some weather dependent enemies are [[Unique Monster (XC3)|Unique Monsters]] that are stronger than minor enemies.
