{{Infobox_NPC |name = Widow |image = Widow.png |personality = |time_active = Anytime |gender = Female |race = |age = 8th Term |location = [[Syra Hovering Reefs]] ([[Colony 11]]) }} '''Widow''' is a NPC in {{XC3}}. Widow can be found in [[Colony 11]].
== Overview == Widow is a part of Colony 11's assault squad, alongside [[Strider]] under the command of their captain [[Zoren]]. She is the squad's sniper, and known for rather unsettling behavior, being the most eager to kill [[Colony Lambda]] soldiers during their squad's attempt to battle with them, and smelling [[Eunie]] up close to tell if she was lying.
== Affinity == * [[Strider]] * [[Zoren]] {{clr}}
